// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0409 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: 910ab35f-8187-5bc2-ae70-245305b0259f

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
